y - Over 40,000 attend Liverpool Pride 2011 |publisher=Liverpool Pride |accessdate=2012-05-24 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511080952/http://www.liverpoolpride.co.uk/news/08/08/2011/proud-mersey-over-40000-attend-liverpool-pride-2011 |archivedate=11 May 2013 }}</ref>  Notable performers included:\n\n{| \n|valign=\"top\"|\n\n; [[Radio City 96.7|Radio City]] Main Stage - [[Pier Head]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.liverpoolpride.co.uk/news/01/08/2011/countdown-begins |title=The Countdown Begins! |publisher=Liverpool Pride |date=1 August 2011 |accessdate=2012-07-08}}</ref>\n# [[Rowetta]]\n# Alan Cross\n# MD Productions\n# Diva Bliss\n# Zara\n# Adam Lyons\n# Sense of Sound\n# Sh-bang\n# Tameka\n# Bears Aloud\n# The Sundaes\n# [[Andi Fraggs]]\n# Sean Rumsey\n# [[Britt Love]]\n# Clubstars + Dance Dynamix\n# [[Kym Mazelle]]\n# Simeon La Mount\n# Beauty\n# Haus of Gaga\n# House of Suarez\n# [[Elouise]]\n# [[Six D]]\n# Chelcee Grimes\n# FTW\n# Gemma Irwin\n# AJ\n# Dance Dynamix\n# Nikki Bell\n\n|valign=\"top\"|\n\n; Summer of Love Stage - [[Pier Head]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.liverpoolpride.co.uk/news/01/08/2011/countdown-begins |title=The Countdown Begins! |publisher=Liverpool Pride |date=1 August 2011 |accessdate=2012-07-08}}</ref>\n# Steve MacFarlane\n# Baby Brave and the Love Bites\n# Sophie Bellamy\n# Jem\n# Jo Bywater\n# Shania\n# Sam Kearney\n# Caz and Brit\n# Karl William Lund\n# TJ and Murphy\n# Rachael Kay\n# RAW Theatre\n# Jay Norton\n# Lonesome Georginas\n# Steve MacFarlane\n# Together\n# Alan Cross\n# Cocabelle\n# Oh My!\n \n|valign=\"top\"|\n\n; Liverpool Pride Fringe Stage \u2013 [[Liverpool gay quarter|Stanley Street]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://musicmafiauk.blogspot.co.uk/2011/08/countdown-begins-to-liverpool-pride.html |title=The Countdown Begins to Liverpool Pride 2011 |publisher=MusicMafia UK |year=2011 |accessdate=2012-07-08}}</ref>\n# Cabaret and DJs from Superstar Boudoir\n# Philip McGuire\n# Lisbon singer Anna Lee\